Package: rgetne
Title: Bayesian Promotion Time Cure Model Toolkit and Interactive App
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R:
    person("Rocio", "Maintainer", email = "rocio@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to fit Bayesian Promotion Time Cure Models
    (Yakovlev & Tsodikov bounded cumulative hazard formulation) via
    Stan, with support for interactions, per-variable priors,
    identifiability diagnostics, clinically oriented visualisations,
    and a companion interactive Shiny application. The package ships
    an example dataset and the compiled Stan model so that the full
    workflow can be reproduced end-to-end.
